These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, software-developer, scientist
1. the software-developer is on the far left##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | software-developer | scientist | dressmaker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, chef, security-guard
1. the security-guard is on the far right##1
2. the coach is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | coach | chef | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | drawing | woodworking | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, spanish
