.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, train
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | train | scooter | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | zombie | horror |

